sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant C as norviq CLI
    participant A as APIClient
    participant N as Norviq API

    U->>C: norviq policy list
    C->>A: get("/api/v1/policies")
    A->>N: HTTP GET /api/v1/policies
    N-->>A: 200 JSON policies
    A-->>C: parsed payload
    C-->>U: table/json output
    C-->>C: log code NRVQ-CLI-8003
